    "Table 5 Publication and reporting bias",
    "Results are based on checks for publication and reporting bias using Egger's test (Egger et al., 1997), Fail-safe N calculations (Orwin, 1983; Rosenberg, 2005), and nonparametric trim-and-fill analysis of the full sample (Duval & Tweedie, 2000a, 2000b).",
